    <text id="A7505T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Evans writes to his brother to ask for help in conducting some personal
                business.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1864-03-16">March 16 1864</date>
                        <name type="place">Camp Stonewall - Prepano</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>D Bro</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I <orig reg="received">Recd</orig> a letter from Home toDay and on the outside it
                    looks like you <unclear>address</unclear> it and if you did I <orig reg="can't"
                        >cant</orig> see <unclear>why</unclear> you did not write to me</p>

                <p>I think the letter was sent to Staunton and you put the <unclear>Envlop</unclear>
                    on it I sent you by (Sergt Lyan) a letter and I wish you would
                    <unclear>answer</unclear> it if you <orig reg="can't">cant</orig> why I will get
                        <orig reg="someone">som one</orig> else to do it</p>

                <p>I Hope you will <orig reg="answer">answe</orig> this and <unclear>send</unclear>
                    me what Information <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> asked you to <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> and let me
                        <orig reg="know">kno</orig> if you can't <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> that <del
                        hand="h1"/> if those <unclear>shoes</unclear> comes to <unclear>Staunton</unclear>
                    <unclear>only</unclear> you keep them until I send for them <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    Dont let anyone <orig reg="steal">steel</orig> them Write Immediately My love to
                    all </p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Yr Bro</salute>
                    <signed>W L Evans</signed>
                    <seg type="postscript">Find Enclosed the letter I Speak of</seg>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
